descriptionHtml:
Hello everyone. 

I have been making Racemenu presets for a long time, just for fun.
I was told that I should start uploading them to the Nexus, so here is my first ever Nexus upload.
Fauriel, the pretty Bosmer wildling. 
She was a side character that I made just for hunting, and now you can have her too!

There are some requirements.
They are not hard requirements, as in she will still load without them, 
but I promise that she will not look the same if you are using other mods.
You can still give it a shot and see how it looks
Most of you guys will be using some of these mods already.
To achieve the same look as the pics, you will need:

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/]Ks Hairdos[/url]﻿
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59192/]Eyes of Aber[/url]﻿
[url=https://seren4xx.tumblr.com/post/99919848365/srg-female-textures-for-over-a-year-youve-been]SRG Female Textures[/url]﻿
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22701/?tab=images]Seductive Lips HD[/url]﻿
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/86208/]Freckle Mania 2
[/url][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7127]Rans Type C Head Mesh
[/url][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411]Brows[/url]
That should be it. 
Feel free to leave any feedback in the comments.
I would love to see pics of her in your game, so please upload some if you use her :)
Enjoy!
author: Froztee
